{"tid":1803302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷設立兩條投訴警暴熱線　將轉介廉署跟進","createTime":"2019-12-30T06:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T11:52:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"82ce53770b456b5bdba39686c9f91a0a238cb9ff","tid":1803302,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500141_1_20191230135129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1500141_1_20191230135129.jpg&h=4c38c0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷指出，廉政公署已經成立專門調查反修例事件警務人員失當行為的「特別調查組」，他已設立兩條投訴警暴熱線，整理所得資料後，會轉介廉署跟進。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷指出，根據一宗1986年對廉政專員的上訴案例，法庭指《廉政公署條例》第12條「貪污行為」也包括公職人員損害公眾利益的罪行及意圖削弱公信力，故他認為廉署有法定職責調查「警察濫權或濫用武力」。<br />\n<br />\n早前3名警員在北區醫院涉嫌虐打一名長者被捕，林卓廷指，他們的控罪其後被改為「公職人員行為失當罪」，他認為現時警隊的濫捕濫權行為，亦有可能干犯相關罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500141-20191230.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500141-20191230.htm&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=e16eb0a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500141-20191230.htm&h=9bb45fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500141-20191230.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c430ad8f0867d9c43261a132c7a1a705f974a99d","tid":1803302,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=07e1c2a3\" target=\"_blank\">https:/